data.description: Alot of character and style was added to this wonderful ranch style home! Vaulted ceilings on the main entrance and great room, with a large open kitchen and corrugated steel accents and a Rustic flare. This home has a total of 5 full bedrooms and 3 of them have walk-in closets. You'll enjoy entertaining here inside and out! Tons of cabinetry and counter space in the kitchen and dining area with a slider out to the deck and patio. There are beautiful lviews of the moutain amongst the professional,landscaping. The main floor offers a huge master bedroom and a 5 piece bathroom. The lower level beautfifully decorated with more rustic accents and has a large hobby and or play room. Both bedrooms are conforming with walk-in closets and a 3/4 bathroom. Contact Donna Martensen @307-262-0461 or donna.realestateleaders247.com
